                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="value-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">‚ö°</div>
                    <h3>Speed + Accuracy</h3>
                    <p>Quick answers without compromising trust. Get insights in hours, not months.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">üéØ</div>
                    <h3>Fit-for-Purpose</h3>
                    <p>Only the features and insights you actually need. No bloated enterprise complexity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">üîó</div>
                    <h3>Integration-Friendly</h3>
                    <p>Works seamlessly with Tally, Zoho, Excel, and tools you already use daily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">üîç</div>
                    <h3>Hidden Patterns</h3>
                    <p>Spot risks and opportunities before they become obvious to competitors.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">üáÆüá≥</div>
                    <h3>Local Intelligence</h3>
                    <p>Understands India's seasonal cycles, regional shifts, and market dynamics.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">üí∞</div>
                    <h3>SMB Pricing</h3>
                    <p>Enterprise AI capabilities at prices that make sense for growing businesses.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="problem-section">
        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5">
            <div class="problem-grid">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-[#2c3e50]">You're Making Decisions Blind</h2>
                    <ul class="problem-list">
                        <li>Excel sheets everywhere, but no clear picture</li>
                        <li>Seasonal patterns surprise you every year</li>
                        <li>Customer churn happens before you notice</li>
                        <li>Inventory decisions based on gut feel</li>
                        <li>Competition moves faster with better insights</li>
                        <li>Enterprise AI solutions cost 10x your budget</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="animate-float">
                    <div class="text-[8rem] text-center opacity-30">üìä</div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-[1.2rem] text-[#2c3e50]">Your data has answers.<br/>You just need the right questions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="solution-section" id="solutions">
        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5">
            <h2 class="section-title">AI Tools That Fit Your Business</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Not the other way around</p>

            <div class="solution-grid">
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-number">01</div>
                    <h3>Connect Your Data</h3>
                    <p>Link your existing systems ‚Äì Tally, Zoho, spreadsheets. No migration headaches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-number">02</div>
