                </div>
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-number">03</div>
                    <h3>Clear Insights</h3>
                    <p>Plain English answers to your business questions. No technical jargon.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-number">04</div>
